---
// src/pages/datenschutz.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Cloud Identity Summit">
    <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 w-full flex-grow">
        <div class="text-blue-500 text-sm font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-3">Legal</div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight mb-12">Privacy Policy</h1>
        
        <div class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed space-y-8">
            
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">1. An Overview of Data Protection</h2>
                <p>The operators of this website take the protection of your personal data very seriously. We treat your personal data as confidential and in accordance with the statutory data protection regulations (GDPR / DSGVO) and this Privacy Policy.</p>
                <p class="mt-2">As a purely static website hosted on modern cloud infrastructure, we do not use tracking cookies, analytics frameworks, or user databases on this site. Your data is only processed where technically necessary to display this website.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">2. Data Controller</h2>
                <p>The party responsible for processing data on this website (the "controller") is:</p>
                <p class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 mt-4 font-mono text-sm">
                    Gregor Reimling<br/>
                    Bicksfeld 11<br/>
                    42699 Solingen<br/>
                    Germany<br/><br/>
                    Email: <span id="privacy-mail-placeholder">[Protected Email]</span>
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">3. Data Collection on our Website</h2>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Hosting and Infrastructure</h3>
                <p>Our website is hosted on Azure Static Web Apps (Microsoft Ireland Operations Limited, One Microsoft Place, South County Business Park, Leopardstown, Dublin 18, Ireland). When you access our website, Microsoft automatically collects data in server log files to ensure technical security and stable operations.</p>
                
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-6 mb-2">Server Log Files</h3>
                <p>The infrastructure automatically records the following technical information transmitted by your browser:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 my-4 pl-4 text-slate-400 text-sm font-mono">
                    <li>Browser type and browser version</li>
                    <li>Operating system used</li>
                    <li>Referrer URL (the page you visited before)</li>
                    <li>Hostname of the accessing computer</li>
                    <li>Time of the server request</li>
                    <li>IP address (anonymized/truncated depending on provider settings)</li>
                </ul>
                <p>The legal basis for this processing is Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR. The website operator has a legitimate interest in the technically error-free presentation and optimization of the website.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">4. Your Rights as a Data Subject</h2>
                <p>Under the GDPR, you have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-4 pl-4 text-slate-400">
                    <li><strong class="text-slate-200">Right to information:</strong> You can ask what personal data we hold about you.</li>
                    <li><strong class="text-slate-200">Right to correction or deletion:</strong> You can request that incorrect data be corrected or completely deleted.</li>
                    <li><strong class="text-slate-200">Right to object:</strong> You have the right to object to the processing of your data based on legitimate interests.</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-4">If you wish to exercise any of these rights, please contact the controller using the email address provided above.</p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script is:inline>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            const user = 'hello';
            const domain = 'identitysummit.cloud';
            const element = document.getElementById('privacy-mail-placeholder');
            if (element) {
                element.innerHTML = `<a href="mailto:${user}@${domain}" class="hover:underline text-blue-400">${user}@${domain}</a>`;
            }
        });
    </script>
</Layout>